  <body>
    <segment id="1" parent="6" relname="span">Darwin as a Geologist</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="8" relname="concession">
He tends to be viewed now as a biologist,</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="8" relname="list">
but in his five years on the Beagle his main work was geology,</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="8" relname="list">
and he saw himself as a geologist.</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="8" relname="list">
His work contributed significantly to the field.</segment>
<group id="6" type="span" />
<group id="8" type="multinuc" parent="9" relname="span" />
<group id="9" type="span" parent="1" relname="evidence" />
